import React from 'react' import { Container, Navbar, Nav} from 'react-bootstrap' import './Navibar.css' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router' import { useState } from 'react' import { toast } from 'react-toastify' const AfterLogNavibar = () => { const navigate = useNavigate() const [show, setShow]= useState(true) let loginRegister const { firstName, loginStatus } = sessionStorage if (firstName != undefined) { loginRegister = `Hello, ${firstName}` } else { loginRegister = "Login" } const logoutUser = () => { sessionStorage.removeItem("id") sessionStorage.removeItem("firstName") sessionStorage.removeItem("lastName") sessionStorage.removeItem("loginStatus") // navigate to sign in component navigate("/") } return (
E-LEARNING
Feedback Profile {/*
*/}
) } export default AfterLogNavibar
